    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a budget-friendly daily driver or a solid base for a project. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings on the passenger side, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all basic electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new brake pads and a suspension tune-up to return it to peak performance. It\u2019s a dependable car for someone willing to put in a little work or looking for affordable transportation.",
      "price": 18500.0,
