    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, a specimen of automotive preservation that transcends the standard pre-owned category. Maintained to a rigorous standard, this motorcar retains its original showroom luster and exhibits no discernible wear, both mechanically and aesthetically. It represents an infrequent opportunity for the serious enthusiast to secure a vehicle of unrivaled pedigree and fastidious upkeep. For those who demand an uncompromising level of quality and performance, this offering stands as the definitive choice.",
